所示。于是待求的定积分可以转化为以下形式（记 
\begin_inset Formula $\nu\coloneqq\ee^{\ii\mathrm{\pi}}$
\end_inset

）：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{0}^{\infty}\frac{x^{\alpha-1}}{x+\nu}\dd{x}=\lim_{R\to\infty}\lim_{\delta\to0}\int_{L_{0}}\frac{z^{\alpha-1}}{z+\nu}\dd{z}=\lim_{R\to\infty}\lim_{\delta\to0}\left(\oint_{C}-\int_{C_{R}}-\int_{C_{\delta}}-\int_{L_{2\mathrm{\pi}}}\right)\frac{z^{\alpha-1}}{z+\nu}\dd{z}
\]

\end_inset

第一项的积分值可以由留数定理得到：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lim_{R\to\infty}\lim_{\delta\to0}\oint_{C}\frac{z^{\alpha-1}}{z+\nu}\dd{z}=2\mathrm{\pi}\ii\eval{\Res\frac{z^{\alpha-1}}{z+\nu}}_{z=-\nu=\ee^{\ii\mathrm{\pi}}\ee^{\ii\phi}}=\left(\ee^{\ii\mathrm{\pi}}\ee^{\ii\phi}\right)^{\alpha-1}2\mathrm{\pi}\ii
\]

\end_inset

这里用到了单值分支上的辐角条件：
\begin_inset Formula $\arg z\in(0,2\mathrm{\pi})$
\end_inset

。第二、三项的积分值均为零，这可以由
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand nameref
reference "lem:大圆弧"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

引理和
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand nameref
reference "lem:小圆弧"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

引理得到：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lim_{\abs{z}\to\infty}z\frac{z^{\alpha-1}}{z+\nu}=\lim_{\abs{z}\to0}z\frac{z^{\alpha-1}}{z+\nu}=0,\quad\alpha\in(0,1)
\]

\end_inset

第四项 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{2\mathrm{\pi}}$
\end_inset

 上的积分与 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{0}$
\end_inset

 上的积分只相差一个常系数：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\int_{L_{0}}\frac{z^{\alpha-1}}{z+\nu}\dd{z} & =\int_{\delta}^{R}\frac{\left(\rho\ee^{\i0}\right)^{\alpha-1}}{\rho\ee^{\i0}+\nu}\dd{\rho\ee^{\i0}}=\int_{\delta}^{R}\frac{\rho^{\alpha-1}}{\rho+\nu}\dd{\rho}\\
\int_{L_{2\mathrm{\pi}}}\frac{z^{\alpha-1}}{z+\nu}\dd{z} & =\int_{R}^{\delta}\frac{\left(\rho\ee^{\i2\mathrm{\pi}}\right)^{\alpha-1}}{\rho\ee^{\i2\mathrm{\pi}}+\nu}\dd{\rho\ee^{\i2\mathrm{\pi}}}=\ee^{\i2\mathrm{\pi}\alpha}\int_{R}^{\delta}\frac{\rho^{\alpha-1}}{\rho+\nu}\dd{\rho}=-\ee^{\i2\mathrm{\pi}\alpha}\int_{L_{0}}\frac{z^{\alpha-1}}{z+\nu}\dd{z}
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

这里的 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho^{\alpha-1}$
\end_inset

 是单值的实变函数。综合以上结果，最终得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{0}^{\infty}\frac{x^{\alpha-1}}{x+\ee^{\ii\phi}}\dd{x}=\frac{\left(\ee^{\ii\mathrm{\pi}}\ee^{\ii\phi}\right)^{\alpha-1}2\mathrm{\pi}\ii}{1-\ee^{\i2\mathrm{\pi}\alpha}}=\frac{\mathrm{\pi}}{\sin\mathrm{\pi}\alpha}\left(\ee^{\ii\phi}\right)^{\alpha-1}
\]

\end_inset

特别地，若 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi=0$
\end_inset

，则
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{0}^{\infty}\frac{x^{\alpha-1}}{x+1}\dd{x}=\frac{\mathrm{\pi}}{\sin\mathrm{\pi}\alpha}
\]

\end_inset


